ash point (in a closed crucible), minimum, °С</td><td>185</td><td>185</td><td>ISO 2592</td></tr><tr><td>Air release properties <sup>4)</sup> at 50 °C, maximum, min.</td><td colspan="2">5</td><td>DIN 9120</td></tr><tr><td>Density at 15 °С, minimum, g/ml</td><td colspan="2">Must be specified by the supplier</td><td>ISO 3675</td></tr><tr><td>Pour point, maximum, °C</td><td colspan="2">-6</td><td>ISO 3016</td></tr><tr><td>Ash (oxide ash), % wt.</td><td colspan="2">Must be specified by the supplier</td><td>ISO 6245</td></tr><tr><td>Water content, max.<span style="white-space: nowrap;">mg/kg</span></td><td colspan="2">150</td><td>ISO 12937</td></tr><tr><td>Purity level, minimum</td><td colspan="2">20/17/14</td><td>ISO 4406</td></tr><tr><td>Foam:</td><td colspan="2">&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Stage 1 at 24 °C, maximum, ml</td><td colspan="2">450/0</td><td>ISO 6247</td></tr><tr><td>Stage II at 93 °C, maximum, ml</td><td colspan="2">100/0</td><td>ISO 6247</td></tr><tr><td>Stage III at 24 °C after 93 °C, maximum, m;</td><td colspan="2">450/0</td><td>ISO 6247</td></tr><tr><td>Water separation (after steam treatment), maximum, s</td><td colspan="2">300</td><td>DIN 51 589-1</td></tr><tr><td>Copper corrosion, maximum Corrosivity (3 h at 125 °C)</td><td colspan="2">2</td><td>ISO 2160</td></tr><tr><td>Oxidation Stability (TOST) <sup>3)</sup> Time in hours to reach delta NZ 2.0 mg KOH/g</td><td colspan="2">3500</td><td>ISO 4263-1</td></tr><tr><td>RPVOT, min</td><td colspan="2">750</td><td>ASTM D2272</td></tr><tr><td>Modified RPVOT, % time minute in unmodified test method, min</td><td colspan="2">85</td><td>ASTM D2272</td></tr></tbody></table><div>'
